desc: We offer a mix of Antique French country Rustic Furniture and accessories from over three centuries. One of a kind objects from churches, farmhouses, chateaus, barns, old industrial mills and factories made from Oak, Elm, Ash, Pine, Pitch Pine, Glass, Pottery, Ceramic, Enamel, Metal ware, Lighting
